"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/620867","Department for Culture, Media and Sport","false","2016-10-31","<p>The Department and Ministers meet regularly with the Welsh Government on areas of common interest - including the proposed review of S4C.</p>","West Suffolk","Matt Hancock",,"2016-10-31T10:34:47.917Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/620867/answer","Biography information for Matt Hancock","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/620867/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/620867/answer",,,,,"10","Culture, Media and Sport","Culture, Media and Sport","2016-10-25","S4C Independent Review","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport, what discussions she has had with the Welsh Government on the review of S4C.","false","Biography information for Hywel Williams","Arfon","Hywel Williams","50293"
